story :
A fisherman from a isolated island in the north of  Malano, which is only inhabited by 12 people, has the task of guarding the dragon egg that became a legend on the island. When suddenly an earthquake occurs on the island, the fishermen try to save the one remaining dragon egg and make it have the power of a dragon egg.
